            <title>[CASSANDRA-16560] Update IDE and Eclipse classpaths for tests (after migration to resolver-ant-tasks)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16560</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
